OL,3,CThe former GB para-athlete hoping to
OL,4,Cski to the South Pole in 40 days
OL,6,FA former GB para-athlete from south
OL,7,FDevon is aiming to become the first
OL,8,Fdisabled person to ski solo and
OL,9,Funsupported to the South Pole- in just
OL,10,F40 days.
OL,12,FJonny Huntington, 38, from Kingsbridge
OL,13,Fsuffered a stroke while serving as an
OL,14,Fofficer in the British Army in 2014.
OL,15,FThe bleed on his brain left him
OL,16,Fcompletely paralysed from the neck
OL,17,Fdown on his left side.
