OL,3,CThe former GB para-athlete hoping to
OL,4,Cski to the South Pole in 40 days
OL,6,FAfter 10 years of rehabilitation and
OL,7,Ftraining he is set to ski 566 miles of
OL,8,FAntarctic tundra - starting his
OL,9,Fadventure on Monday 11 November.
OL,11,FHe will be dragging all his equipment
OL,12,Fand food in a sled which will weigh in
OL,13,Fexcess of 110kg.
OL,15,FMr Huntington said: "No one with a
OL,16,Fdisability has done this before so I
OL,17,Ffind it quite exciting. I'll be doing
OL,18,Fit completely on my own with no sort
OL,19,Fof help, no resupply, nothing like
OL,20,Fthat.
