OL,3,CThe former GB para-athlete hoping to
OL,4,Cski to the South Pole in 40 days
OL,6,F"You sort of get thrown out of a plane
OL,7,Fat one end and you hopefully wind up
OL,8,Fat the other end, 40 days later.
OL,10,F"Existing somewhere which is
OL,11,Ffundamentally hostile to life, it's
OL,12,Fthe ultimate test."
OL,14,FThe former army officer was just eight
OL,15,Fweeks into his role when he suffered a
OL,16,Fbleed on the brain.
OL,18,FIt took years of rehabilitation before
OL,19,Fhe was able to fully walk again, and
OL,20,Feven then he was left with restricted
OL,21,Fmovement down his left side.
