OL,3,CThe former GB para-athlete hoping to
OL,4,Cski to the South Pole in 40 days
OL,6,FHe has also been left with permanent
OL,7,Fbrain damage.
OL,9,F"When I was about two years post
OL,10,Finjury and had just been discharged
OL,11,Ffrom the military, I experienced some
OL,12,Fpretty poor mental health." said Mr
OL,13,FHuntington.
OL,15,F"A significant aspect of it came about
OL,16,Fbecause I had lost sight of what I
OL,17,Ffelt I was meant to be working
OL,18,Ftowards."
