OL,3,CThe former GB para-athlete hoping to
OL,4,Cski to the South Pole in 40 days
OL,6,FDuring his recovery, he became a
OL,7,Fmember of the Armed Forces Para-
OL,8,FSnowsport Team (AFPST), which ignited
OL,9,Fhis love for skiing.
OL,11,FMr Huntington went on to join the GB
OL,12,FPara Nordic ski team, where he
OL,13,Fcompeted from 2017 to 2020 at World
OL,14,FCups in Lviv, Ukraine, and Vuokatti,
OL,15,FFinland, as well as the inaugural
OL,16,FEuropean Paralympic Committee Games in
OL,17,FPoland in 2020.
OL,19,FThe idea for his South Pole expedition
OL,20,Fwas planted after he stopped skiing
OL,21,Fcompetitively.
