OL,3,CThe former GB para-athlete hoping to
OL,4,Cski to the South Pole in 40 days
OL,6,FHe has since taken on a number of
OL,7,Fchallenges to prepare for the venture,
OL,8,Fincluding running the entirety of the
OL,9,F630 mile South West Coast Path, from
OL,10,FSomerset to Dorset.
OL,12,FHe also undertook a 20-day solo
OL,13,Fexpedition in northern Sweden in April.
OL,15,FFor his Antarctic challenge, Mr
OL,16,FHuntington will fly into Union Glacier
OL,17,Fwhere he will spend a few days on the
OL,18,Fice to complete his final preparations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
