OL,3,CThe former GB para-athlete hoping to
OL,4,Cski to the South Pole in 40 days
OL,6,FHe will then take a final short flight
OL,7,Fto the start of the expedition where
OL,8,Fhe will set off from Fuchs-Messner on
OL,9,Fthe edge of the Antarctic landmass and
OL,10,Fski solo and unsupported to the South
OL,11,FPole.
OL,13,F"I know that I know what I'm doing,
OL,14,Fand I also know, having spoken to
OL,15,Fother people who have done successful
OL,16,Fexpeditions, that I have done the
OL,17,Fright level of preparation," Mr
OL,18,FHuntington added
