OL,3,CThe former GB para-athlete hoping to
OL,4,Cski to the South Pole in 40 days
OL,6,F"I've done everything I can to make it
OL,7,Fsucceed, but I've never been to
OL,8,FAntarctica before, it famously has
OL,9,Fquite strict conditions down there.
OL,11,F"There aren't disabled explorers, it's
OL,12,Fnot a job, but I'll just have to
OL,13,Ffigure out how we can make this work."
